OL,3,CIncrease capital cash in Budget,
OL,4,CRobison tells Chancellor Reeves
OL,6,FAhead of the debate, Ms Robison said:
OL,7,F"We have been clear that Scotland
OL,8,Ffaces a deeply challenging financial
OL,9,Fsituation as a result of rising costs
OL,10,Fand global instability, and I will be
OL,11,Fupdating Parliament today on the
OL,12,Fmeasures we are taking to keep our
OL,13,Ffinances on a sustainable footing in
OL,14,Fthe face of these challenges.
OL,16,F"However, there is only so far we can
OL,17,Fgo within our limited powers.
