OL,3,CIncrease capital cash in Budget,
OL,4,CRobison tells Chancellor Reeves
OL,6,F"Funding for hospitals, schools,
OL,7,Ftransport and other infrastructure is
OL,8,Fvital for economic growth and cutting
OL,9,Femissions, so it is important that the
OL,10,FChancellor uses the autumn Budget to
OL,11,Fdeliver sustainable funding for the
OL,12,Ffuture and significantly increases
OL,13,Fcapital funding."
OL,15,FThe UK Government has been contacted
OL,16,Ffor comment.
