OL,4,CRobison tells Chancellor Reeves
OL,6,FMs Robison's comments come after
OL,7,FScottish Labour leader, Anas Sarwar,
OL,8,Fsaid on Monday the Budget will "end
OL,9,Fthe era of austerity" and provide
OL,10,Ffunding for local services.
OL,12,FWhile Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fsaid on Monday that expected tax rises
OL,14,Fin the Budget will "prevent austerity
OL,15,Fand rebuild public services" as he
OL,16,Fstressed that "better days are ahead".
