OL,6,FHe added that "the time is long
OL,7,Foverdue for politicians in this
OL,8,Fcountry to level with you honestly
OL,9,Fabout the trade-offs this country
OL,10,Ffaces, to stop insulting your
OL,11,Fintelligence with the chicanery of
OL,12,Feasy answers".
OL,14,FA Treasury spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,FChancellor has vowed to lead the most
OL,16,Fpro-growth Treasury in history and has
OL,17,Fbeen clear that it is important that
OL,18,Fwe count the benefits of public
OL,19,Finvestment and not just the cost of it.
